            <scopecontent>
                <p>This is a collection of commonplace books kept by Sarah and Susan H. Loyd.
                    Volumes contain poetry, extracts from letters, and numerous entries on religious
                    topics. The collection also contains a receipt book belonging to William Brown,
                    great-great-grandfather of Helen Baily. </p>
